say they have grown closer because of their tennis. ; Photo, Years of club play 
prepared Patti, left, for the demands of doubles play. Elise, right, supplies 
the pair's power and speed. ; Photo, When Patti Nakawatase, second from right, 
heard Moorpark needed tennis players, she agreed to help and a winning doubles 
team was born. MARILYN WEISS / for The Times 
</P>
