SOUNDINGS 
</P>
<P>
From William Endicott in the Sacramento Bee, commenting on Willie Brown's 
opposition to Proposition 119, the redistricting initiative supported by the 
League of Women Voters: 
</P>
<P>
 "It's understandable that Assembly Speaker Willie Brown is at odds with the 
League of Women Voters. The league believes in good government." 
</P>
