</P>
<P>
"These campaigns have become a black box. On one side you put in dollar bills, 
and on the other side you run out videotape." 
</P>
<P>
 -- Darry Sragow, manager of Dianne Feinstein's campaign for the Democratic 
nomination for governor. 
