RELATIONS -- WEST GERMANY; EAST GERMANY -- FOREIGN RELATIONS -- USSR; USSR -- 
FOREIGN RELATIONS -- WEST GERMANY; UNITED STATES -- FOREIGN RELATIONS -- USSR; 
EUROPE -- DEFENSE; ARMS CONTROL; NUCLEAR WEAPONS -- WEST GERMANY; CHEMICAL 
WEAPONS -- WEST GERMANY 
</P>
