closed in the wake of the worst rain inTexas in decades. At least three people 
have been killed since the heavy storms began. Flooding was also widespread in 
Arkansas and Oklahoma, above, where ranchers worked to rescue stranded 
livestock. Associated Press 
</P>
</GRAPHIC>
