<TEXT>
<P>
Keri Phebus of Corona del Mar High School won her second-round match in the 
18-and-under division, 6-0, 6-3, over Erica Kuttler of St. Petersburg, Fla., 
Thursday at the Seventeen magazine Tennis Tournament of Champions in Mission 
Viejo. 
