perform. ; Photo, A singer entertains at weekend pre-Cinco de Mayo celebration. 
Behind him, a banner touts one of the event's commercial sponsors. ; Photo, 
Vivien Bonzo, here with another Olvera Street merchant, says: "I want my people 
to leave Olvera Street with pride, not products. LEO JARZOMB; Photo, COLOR, 
