Zoltan Toth and was selected MVP of the championship series. ; Photo, The 
Sockers' goalie Victor Nogueira says: "A game is a game. I'm not going to get 
hypertension because of a game." ; Photo, Zoltan Toth returned in style with a 
3.48 goals-against average. Los Angeles Times 
</P>
</GRAPHIC>
